Title: Rupee slips 10 paise in early trade
Content: Rupee was trading lower by 10 paise at 66.86 against the U.S. dollar in early trade at the Interbank Foreign Exchange on Thursday.Dealers attributed the rupee’s fall to increased demand for the U.S.
